com.linecorp.armeria.spring

Class ArmeriaSettings

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.linecorp.armeria.spring.ArmeriaSettings

  • @ConfigurationProperties(prefix="armeria")
 @Validated
public class ArmeriaSettings
extends Object
    Settings for armeria servers, e.g., 
    
 armeria:
   ports:
   - port: 8080
     protocol: HTTP
   - ip: 127.0.0.1
     port: 8081
     protocol:HTTP
    TODO(ide) Adds SSL and virtualhost settings
